National Daily reports that Bianca Ojukwu, slapped Ebelechukwu Obiano, the wife of the former governor of Anambra state, this happened during Charles Soludo’s inauguration.
According to report, Ebelechukwu provoked Bianca Ojukwu and called her names, Bianca, in turn, responded by slapping Ebelechukwu, people who were present at the swearing-had to intervene to prevent the issue from escalating.
Reno Omokri, a former presidential aide, took to his YouTube channel to discuss what happened between Bianca and Ebelechukwu. He Stated that Ebele should not sue Bianca because it was a clear case of provocation, and that provocation mitigates any offence, he also stated that in the common law in England, the act of provocation is an offence.
He further revealed that that Ebele approached Bianca first, therefore Bianca has the higher ground, and if she wants she can sue Ebele bedause she is blameless.
